  "texts": [
    "The survey also sought to evaluate the frequency with which participants utilize ChatGPT for their study routines.",
    "Notably, the findings showcased a diverse pattern of usage.",
    "We can identify that most of the participants with 42% using ChatGPT a few times per month, indicating a periodic reliance on the tool.",
    "While 34% of participants revealed a more frequent pattern of usage, relying on ChatGPT several times per week (see Figure 3).",
    "These results underscore the versatility of ChatGPT, catering to a variety of study habits and preferences among the participants."
